    <id>tag:www.gov.uk,2005:PublicationesquePresenter/56798</id>
    <published>2012-07-17T01:00:00+01:00</published>
    <updated>2012-12-17T10:34:19+00:00</updated>
    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/department-for-transport-statement-of-new-regulations"/>
    <title>Department for Transport statement of new regulation</title>
    <category>Publication</category>
    <summary>An overview of regulations planned to be implemented or removed by Department for Transport between 1 January and 30 June 2013.</summary>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;h2 id="fifth-statement-of-new-regulation"&gt;Fifth statement of new regulation&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This statement contains a list of all Department for Transport’s regulatory measures that are in scope of one-in, two-out and are due to be introduced between January – June 2013. For the first time this statement also includes all Red Tape Challenge and EU measures requiring UK legislation, expected to come in over the same period.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id="fourth-statement-of-new-regulation"&gt;Fourth statement of new regulation&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Fourth statement of new regulation provides a picture of domestic regulatory measures that have been introduced or are due to be introduced between July and December 2012 that are in scope of one-in, one-out. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id="third-statement-of-new-regulation"&gt;Third statement of new regulation&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Third statement of new regulation provides a picture of domestic regulatory measures that have been introduced or are due to be introduced between January and June 2012 that are in scope of one-in, one-out.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id="second-statement-of-new-regulation"&gt;Second statement of new regulation&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Second statement of new regulation provides a picture of domestic regulatory measures that have been introduced or are due to be introduced between July and December 2011 that are in scope of one-in, one-out.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id="first-statement-of-new-regulation"&gt;First statement of new regulation&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://www.bis.gov.uk/policies/bre/better-regulation-framework/one-in-one-out/statement"&gt;One-in, one-out statement of new regulation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
