    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/department-for-transport-business-plan"/>
    <title>Department for Transport business plan</title>
    <category>Publication</category>
    <summary>The DfT business plan 2012 to 2015, including monthly progress updates against the actions set out in the structural reform plan.</summary>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;This 2012-15 business plan sets out the programme of work we plan to carry out over the next three years to support the coalition government’s objectives. It also contains information on our structure and budget, and the way we measure our performance.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The full plan is available to download along with annexes. This year’s business plan is an update of the business plan published in May 2011. The full list of actions and indicators in the 2011 plan, with details of any changes made in this revision, is available to view in the &lt;abbr title="Department for Transport"&gt;DfT&lt;/abbr&gt; 2011 business plan revisions table.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The structural reform plan section can be viewed on the updated &lt;a rel="external" href="http://transparency.number10.gov.uk/"&gt;Number 10 transparency website&lt;/a&gt;, with information on the current status of each action, and explanations for any deadlines missed, updated monthly. The &lt;a rel="external" href="http://transparency-archive.number10.gov.uk/transparency/srp/"&gt;previous version of the Number 10 transparency website&lt;/a&gt; hosts the final set of updates for May 2012.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id="may-2011-business-plan-and-annexes"&gt;May 2011 Business Plan and annexes&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20121025123854/http://assets.dft.gov.uk/publications/business-plan-2011-2015/DFT-Business-Plan.pdf"&gt;&lt;abbr title="Department for Transport"&gt;DfT&lt;/abbr&gt; business plan (PDF 334 KB), May 2011&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20121025123854/http://assets.dft.gov.uk/publications/business-plan-2011-2015/DfT-annexa.pdf"&gt;Annex A: Common areas of spend data (PDF, 212 KB)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20121025123854/http://assets.dft.gov.uk/publications/business-plan-2011-2015/DfT-annexb.pdf"&gt;Annex B: Changes to structural reform plan (PDF, 18 KB)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="monthly-updates"&gt;Monthly updates&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The department publishes monthly updates on progress against business plan actions. From June 2012 these updates will be published on the &lt;a rel="external" href="http://transparency.number10.gov.uk/business-plan/11"&gt;Number 10 transparency website&lt;/a&gt;. The May 2012 progress report below is reported against the May 2011 business plan. Some of the actions have now been updated in the May 2012 business plan. For a full list of changes to the May 2011 business plan actions please see the business plan revisions table.&lt;/p&gt;

