  <entry>
    <id>tag:www.gov.uk,2005:PublicationesquePresenter/14074</id>
    <published>2012-02-15T00:00:00+00:00</published>
    <updated>2012-11-10T12:10:35+00:00</updated>
    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/department-for-transport-equality-monitoring"/>
    <title>Department for Transport equality monitoring</title>
    <category>Publication</category>
    <summary>Summary of findings from the staff survey into equality and diversity.</summary>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;h2 id="full-equality-monitoring-reports"&gt;2011 full equality monitoring reports&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;An analysis of staff diversity, for staff in post between 1 April 2010 and 31 March 2011. The analysis looks at staff in post, cessations, grievances and discipline, training, sickness absence, performance markings and recruitment, and considers whether there were significant differences with respect to sex, race, disability, pay band, age, sexual orientation, religion and belief and working pattern.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20120215172540/http://assets.dft.gov.uk/publications/equality-monitoring/report.pdf"&gt;Department for Transport equality monitoring 2010 to 2011 full report (PDF, 129KB)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20120215172540/http://assets.dft.gov.uk/publications/equality-monitoring/annex.xls"&gt;Department for Transport equality monitoring 2010 to 2011 full report annexes (XLS)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20120215172540/http://assets.dft.gov.uk/publications/equality-monitoring/annex-csv.csv"&gt;Department for Transport equality monitoring 2010 to 2011 full report annexes (CSV)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="equality-monitoring-in-the-transport-agencies"&gt;Equality monitoring in the transport agencies&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20120215172540/http://www.dft.gov.uk/publications/dvla-equality-monitoring-2011"&gt;Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency (DVLA)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="/government/publications/equality-monitoring-in-dsa-2010-11"&gt;Driving Standards Agency (DSA)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20120215172540/http://www.dft.gov.uk/publications/gcda-equality-monitoring-2011"&gt;Government Car and Dispatch Agency (GSDA)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/*/http://www.dft.gov.uk/publications/ha-equality-monitoring-2011"&gt;Highways Agency (HA)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
